killsuru (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * kill() wrapper for bash and zsh, enabled system-wide for interactive
    shells via /etc/profile.d, /etc/bash.bashrc and /etc/zsh/zshrc.
  * killsuru(1) helper command to render the SUSURUTV ASCII art, with
    per-user override and color support.

 -- Akira Morooka <0825araakimoro@gmail.com>  Wed, 17 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0900
